{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_12_01",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 あんなのぴょーんですわ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "アリス！　私がアリスですわよ！\n『劇団★見』の主演ですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alice! I am Alice‚ you know!\nThe leading star of “Troupe★Hoshimi” no less!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "聞いたぞ。今度のライブで、雫とすずのダブル主演で\n不思議の国のアリスがモチーフの舞台を演じるんだよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard. At the next live‚ you and Shizuku will be co-starring\nin a stage play themed around Alice in Wonderland‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……大丈夫か？\n演技の経験は、以前連ドラに出演した一回きりだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… are you going to be okay?\nYour acting experience is limited to that one TV drama you did before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "今や私はBIG4！　つまりは大女優成宮すずですわ！\n不安は捨てて大船に乗った気持ちでいてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am now one of the BIG4! In other words‚ the great actress Suzu Narumiya!\nCast aside your worries and sit back with complete confidence!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7611111004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "随分と大きく出たな\n大女優はさすがに言い過ぎじゃないか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re making some pretty bold claims.\n“Great actress” might be a bit much‚ don’t you think…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "細かいことを言わないでくださいまし\n私のこの自信は過信ではありませんのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don’t nitpick over such trivial details.\nThis confidence of mine is not overconfidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8558907191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "なぜならこの私、不思議の国のアリスならば\n幼い頃に劇で演じたことがあるんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because when it comes to Alice in Wonderland‚\nI played it on stage when I was little!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6558907191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったのか……\nそれでその劇はどうだったんだ？　好評だったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see…\nSo how was that play? Was it well received?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、当然ですわ！\n私が出たおかげであの劇は大成功したのですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ of course it was!\nThanks to my appearance‚ the play was a huge success!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9958904902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "舞台の真ん中に堂々と立って、燦然と輝く私に\n観客はみんな、釘付けでしたの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As I stood proudly at center stage‚ shining brilliantly‚\nthe audience couldn’t take their eyes off me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4958859125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "終幕と共に浴びせられる大喝采……\nスタンディングオベーションする観客達の姿！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thunderous applause that rained down at curtain call…\nThe sight of the audience rising for a standing ovation!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6625571568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "あの輝かしい成功は忘れられませんの\n今もあの景色が目に浮かびますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I could never forget that glorious success.\nEven now‚ I can clearly picture that scene.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1292258579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、当時の私と出会っていなかったのが\n本当に惜しいですわね、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu‚ it’s truly a shame that you\nnever got to meet me back then‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7625591913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……もう既にアリス役を演じていたのか\n心配は杞憂だったみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… so you’d already played Alice before.\nSeems my worries were unfounded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "ん……アリス役？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm… Alice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3177082061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、ビデオか何かに記録は残っていないのか？\n優や琴乃、雫の参考になるかもしれないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh right—do you have a video recording or something?\nIt might help Yu‚ Kotono‚ and Shizuku as a reference…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　い、いや、残念なことにお父様も\nお母様も感動のあまり録画を忘れていまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? W-well‚ unfortunately‚ my father\nand mother were so moved they forgot to record it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4546284357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、それは残念だ……\nでも、今思えばぴったりの配役だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ that’s too bad…\nStill‚ now that I think about it‚ it really is perfect casting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "確かにすずの髪型や雰囲気も\nどことなくアリスに似ている気がするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your hairstyle and overall vibe\ndo kind of resemble Alice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "え、えっと、そ、そうですわ！\nもはやアリス役は私の天命ですの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ um‚ y-yes‚ indeed!\nThe role of Alice is my destiny!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7252521197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "動きが多くて大変な役だと思っていたが\n穴に落ちる演技も経験済みなら安心だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it’d be a demanding role with lots of movement‚\nbut if you’ve already done the falling-into-a-hole bit‚ that’s reassuring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.1333272298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと、あ、ああ！\nウサギの穴に飛び込むシーンですわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-um‚ ah—ah yes!\nYou mean the scene where she jumps into the rabbit hole‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1010065078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "あんなのぴょーんですわ！\nふわっとしてぴょんぴょーんですの！　余裕ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s just a hop!\nYou go all floaty and boing-boing—easy peasy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6010258357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　どうしたすず。やけに汗をかいている\n気がするんだが、具合でも悪いのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What’s wrong‚ Suzu? You’re sweating an awful lot.\nAre you feeling unwell or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.9990207463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "え、えっと、そ、そうですわね……\n練習の疲れが出てしまったのかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ um‚ y-yes‚ perhaps…\nMaybe the fatigue from practice caught up with me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.6210282326,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10799.989318900003,
          "startTime": 194.4210175515
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "今日はもう失礼いたしますわね\nアリス役、この成宮すずに任せてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be taking my leave for today.\nPlease leave the role of Alice to me‚ Narumiya Suzu!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.7876948993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "すず、どうしたんだ……？\nゆっくり休んでくれればいいんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ what’s going on with you…?\nI hope you’ll get some good rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後、劇団★見の練習終わりにて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Several days later‚ after Troupe★Hoshimi’s rehearsal",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.689155348,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1933.336385299981,
          "startTime": 204.6224917333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1933.336385299981,
          "startTime": 204.6224917333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 204.4224937676
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
